comments: Barnes (TOR) slides his hand across and off Collins' (ATL) body during the drive, and the contact is marginal.
VanVleet's (TOR) left-hand makes clean contact with the ball as his right makes marginal contact with Collins' (ATL) body before making contact with the ball thereafter.
Siakam (TOR) establishes himself in a screening position in Bogdanovic's (ATL) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Bogdanovic (ATL) slides his hand off Trent Jr.'s (TOR) body during the hand-off, and the contact is marginal.
Bogdanovic (ATL) legally contests Trent Jr.'s (TOR) jump shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Replay review of the foul called on Siakam (TOR) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Siakam (TOR) makes contact with Collins' (ATL) arm prior to making any contact with the ball.
Collins (ATL) and VanVleet (TOR) briefly engage and disengage with one another prior to the inbound pass.
Okongwu (ATL) makes marginal contact with Anunoby (TOR) as he releases toward the basket.
Barnes (TOR) makes contact with Hunter's (ATL) arm and affects his driving shot attempt before the block by Anunoby (TOR).
Siakam (TOR) briefly engages with Collins (ATL) off-ball.
Trent Jr. (TOR) legally contests Bogdanovic's (ATL) jump shot attempt, and incidental contact occurs after his release.
Bogdanovic (ATL) places and retracts his arm from Trent Jr.'s (TOR) body on the perimeter, and the contact is marginal.
Bogdanovic (ATL) legally contests Trent Jr.'s (TOR) jump shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Okongwu (ATL) establishes himself in a screening position in Trent Jr.'s (TOR) path and makes marginal contact as he rolls toward the basket.
Hunter (ATL) does not control the ball on his initial touch. He then gathers it and legally takes a controlled dribble.
Okongwu (ATL) makes marginal contact with Barnes (TOR) underneath the basket as Barnes secures the rebound.
Siakam (TOR) is already in Huerter's (ATL) path and absorbs the body contact during the pick.
Okongwu (ATL) places his hand to VanVleet's (TOR) back during his drive to the basket and marginal contact occurs.
Gallinari (ATL) establishes himself in a screening position in Trent Jr.'s (TOR) path and absorbs the contact.
Bogdanovic (ATL) establishes himself in a screening position in Anunoby's (TOR) path and slightly extends his arm as he releases from the contact.
Siakam (TOR) legally contest Bogdanovic's (ATL) jump shot attempt.
Hunter (ATL) commits a take foul on VanVleet (TOR).
Huerter (ATL) commits  take foul on Siakam (TOR).
Siakam (TOR) and Gallinari (ATL) both engage and separate as Gallinari releases to receive the pass.
Collins (ATL) establishes himself in a screening position in Trent Jr.'s (TOR) path and makes marginal contact as they disengage.
Siakam (TOR) moves alongside Gallinari's (ATL) path during the drive.
Gallinari (ATL) commits a take foul on Siakam (TOR). The take foul occurs prior to any contact by Siakam.
